    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for a daily driver. The engine and transmission are in good working order, providing a steady and dependable ride. However, please note there is some visible wear on the interior upholstery and minor scratches on the exterior paint. It is up to date on basic maintenance, though it may soon require routine service for tires and brakes. Overall, it's a solid car for someone looking for functionality at a reasonable price.",
