      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained over the years. The exterior is clean, though it shows some minor signs of age such as small stone chips on the front fascia and a few light surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is well-preserved with no major tears or stains, and all electronics are fully functional. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
