    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This car is ready for some serious TLC and could be the perfect restoration opportunity for a dedicated enthusiast! While it is currently in poor condition and needs significant work, it offers a great foundation for someone looking to build their dream ride from the ground up. Grab this chance to breathe new life into a classic project!",
